sourcesContent: import { Component, OnInit } from '@angular/core'; import { FormGroup } from '@angular/forms'; @Component({ selector: 'app-login', templateUrl: './login.component.html', styleUrls: ['./login.component.css'] }) export class LoginComponent implements OnInit { loginForm!:FormGroup ngOnInit(): void { this.loginForm=new FormGroup({ email:new Form }) } }
